data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Sort Order specifies the order in which the menu items will appear. The Add Separator value defines whether a menu separator will be drawn; this allows for grouping of activities whithin one menu. If a menu item is not included in a rendered menu (e.g. Office created only accessible for certain file/meta types), a separator will still be drawn if the menu item's Add Separator value is checked.
